title: Buccaneers vs Panthers recap, Week 2 Preview
itunes:title: Buccaneers vs Panthers recap, Week 2 Preview
description:
Come back to this feed after the end of the Thursday Night Football game to hear the recap! A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Chris Wesseling, Marc Sessler and Gregg Rosenthal spin through every single game leading up to week 2 in the NFL. As Gregg was the only one who won his lock last week, he gets to draft first in the game selection and Dan makes an unexpected rule change at the top of the show. It's a sad, sad day to be a Jets fan and we get to hear from Keith Hanzus.
